# Consent and change-control

This repository follows an explicit consent model.

## Baseline

- Changes to protected context (`docs/_core/**`, org baseline paths) require owner consent.
- Project-local specialization is allowed when it tightens controls.
- Any weakening deviation must be recorded and approved.

## Evidence

- Record approval links in PR/MR discussions.
- Keep deviations in `docs/project/governance_overlay.md` when applicable.
